icon.entries: "$wi(icon)$"##Current,"$wf(icon, 0)$"##Today Forecast,"$wf(icon, 1)$"##Tomorrow Forecast,"$wf(icon, 2)$"##2 Days Forecast,"$wf(icon, 3)$"##3 Days Forecast,"$wf(icon, 4)$"##4 Days Forecast,"$wf(icon, 5)$"##5 Days Forecast,"$wf(icon, 6)$"##6 Days Forecast,"$wf(icon, 7)$"##7 Days Forecast,"$wf(icon, 8)$"##8 Days Forecast,"$wf(icon, 9)$"##9 Days Forecast
